{"tid":2385860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"校長羅婉儀：「我想講，個官講嘅嘢，同事實係有距離嘅」","createTime":"2021-01-29T08:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T15:35:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e678545222060b83bf292f00893275201b20f1bd","tid":2385860,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/229657612047010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F229657612047010&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=3971af8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/229657612047010</a><br />\n<br />\n天水圍東華三院李東海小學老師林麗棠前年 3 月於校內墮樓身亡，死因庭今早裁決。死因裁判官周慧珠在判詞中批評時任校長羅婉儀對林「咬住唔放」，事發前一天再召見林老師導致其精神崩潰，觸發林老師輕生，又指悲劇原可以避免。<br />\n<br />\n羅婉儀離開法庭時，以漁夫帽及雨傘遮擋，從西九龍調解中心後門離開。多名記者追訪她會否向家屬道歉；認為自己對林老師的死有無責任等。<br />\n<br />\n羅婉儀僅回應一句指：「我想講，個官講嘅嘢，同事實係有距離嘅」；不過一名男親友隨即阻止羅婉儀說：「唔好講啦唔好講啦！」記者再追問羅意指判詞哪一部分，及是否認為裁判官針對她，羅婉儀未有再回應。"},{"pid":"b01cd3747b281e719821644d536b0c181bf67abd","tid":2385860,"uid":29153,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"林鄭style"},{"pid":"cf789bdeeb8493ba07d232453004ef40148ad1a1","tid":2385860,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf399c551358df7d0bad06c2381baaf5c7d9278","tid":2385860,"uid":95577,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"我想講，你唔仆街死都無撚用"},{"pid":"8afcfa7a867e66033efd2f354816c41f9748bc6e","tid":2385860,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4